******************************
*****
*****  BCPL PROGRAMMING  *****
*****
******************************

BCPL was created by Martin Richards at Cambridge University in 1967. It is a very basic
"keep it simple" computer programming language that influenced later computer programming
languages such as C and C++.


Links:

http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/users/mr/BCPL.html
http://www.nordier.com/software/bcpl.html
http://rosettacode.org/wiki/BCPL
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BCPL


Books:

ISBN-13: 9780521785433 -- BCPL: THE LANGUAGE AND ITS COMPILER